## 4. Data Flow — Backend Pull Cycle (Extension Not Involved)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Cron as FleetEdgeCronService<br/>(every ~4h)
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant Proxy as FleetEdgeProxyService
    participant CVP as FleetEdge CVP API
    participant FCS as FuelComparisonService
    participant SW as Extension SW<br/>(statusPoll alarm)

    Cron->>DB: Find ACTIVE tokens with expiresAt > now
    loop Per account
        Cron->>DB: Decrypt freshest token
        Cron->>Proxy: Pull vehicle data (uses JWT)
        alt FleetEdge 401/403
            Proxy-->>Cron: Auth failed
            Cron->>DB: Token.status = NEEDS_REAUTH
            Cron->>DB: Write FLEETEDGE_REAUTH_REQUIRED UserError
        else Success
            Proxy->>CVP: vehicle master / fuel data
            CVP-->>Proxy: Telemetry
            Proxy->>FCS: Compute variance & odometer check
            FCS->>DB: Store results<br/>(FuelComparisonTask → COMPLETED)
        end
    end
    Cron->>DB: Record pull status<br/>{lastRunAt, nextRunAt, pullingNow}

    Note over SW: ~2 minutes later
    SW->>DB: GET /fleetedge/status + /status
    DB-->>SW: {accounts, pull, metrics}
    SW->>SW: Update popup state + badge
```

