## 5. Token Expiry & Re-Auth Loop

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Cron as Backend Cron
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant SW as Extension SW
    actor User
    participant FE as FleetEdge Tab

    Note over DB: Predictive: expiresAt <= now<br/>Definitive: FleetEdge 401 on pull
    Cron->>DB: Mark token NEEDS_REAUTH
    Cron->>DB: Write FLEETEDGE_REAUTH_REQUIRED error

    SW->>DB: GET /fleetedge/status (alarm poll)
    DB-->>SW: Account.status = NEEDS_REAUTH
    SW->>SW: Card → red "Expired"<br/>Badge → red count<br/>chrome.notifications.create

    User->>FE: Opens FleetEdge, logs in
    User->>SW: Clicks "Reconnect"
    Note over SW: Same capture flow as link-token
    SW->>DB: POST /fleetedge/link-token → ACTIVE
    SW->>SW: Card → green, notification cleared
```

