## 7. LEMU Telemetry Layers

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph LEMU["LEMU — 7 Layer Telemetry"]
        UI["UI Layer<br/>User interactions, popup events"]
        MSG["MESSAGE Layer<br/>sendMessage types, handlers"]
        BE["BACKEND Layer<br/>API calls, responses, errors"]
        FE["FLEETEDGE Layer<br/>Token capture, link status"]
        STOR["STORAGE Layer<br/>chrome.storage operations"]
        TOK["TOKEN Layer<br/>JWT read, expiry checks"]
        TASK["TASK Layer<br/>Process triggers, results"]
    end

    subgraph Buffer["In-Memory Buffer"]
        BUF["Event Buffer<br/>(max 2000 events)"]
    end

    subgraph Storage["chrome.storage.local"]
        SL["telemetry_events<br/>+ health_snapshot"]
    end

    subgraph BackendShip["Backend Shipment"]
        SHIP["POST /telemetry/ingest<br/>batched 25 events<br/>every 60s<br/>WARN+ severity only"]
    end

    UI --> BUF
    MSG --> BUF
    BE --> BUF
    FE --> BUF
    STOR --> BUF
    TOK --> BUF
    TASK --> BUF

    BUF -->|"flush every 5s"| SL
    SL -->|"ship every 60s"| SHIP
```

